<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>How to Use</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.6.0/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        .step {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(20px);
            transition: all 0.6s ease-in-out;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 500;
            padding: 15px;
            border-left: 4px solid #007bff;
            background: white;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .step.visible {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
        .step strong {
            color: #007bff;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('navbar2.ejs') %>

    <header class="text-center mt-5">
        <h1 class="fw-bold">How to Use the Facial Analysis Tool</h1>
    </header>

    <main class="container mt-4">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-8">
                <ol class="list-unstyled">
                    <li class="step"><strong>Step 1:</strong> Capture a clear, well-lit front-facing image of your face.</li>
                    <li class="step"><strong>Step 2:</strong> Take a side-angle photo for a more detailed analysis.</li>
                    <li class="step"><strong>Step 3:</strong> Capture a close-up image focusing on your skin texture.</li>
                    <li class="step"><strong>Step 4:</strong> Upload all three images using the provided upload button.</li>
                    <li class="step"><strong>Step 5:</strong> Click "Analyze" to begin the AI-based facial assessment.</li>
                    <li class="step"><strong>Step 6:</strong> The system will process your images within a few seconds.</li>
                    <li class="step"><strong>Step 7:</strong> View a detailed skin analysis report with personalized recommendations.</li>
                    <li class="step"><strong>Step 8:</strong> Download the report as a PDF for future reference.</li>
                    <li class="step"><strong>Step 9:</strong> Repeat the analysis weekly to monitor skin progress.</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <script>
        $(document).ready(function() {
            $(".step").each(function(index) {
                setTimeout(() => {
                    $(this).addClass("visible");
                }, index * 250);
            });
        });
    </script>

    <%- include('footer.ejs') %>
</body>
</html>
